title: Secret Baby
description: Nanny to the rescue? Blaine gets a knock on his door. It's his ex-girlfriend from about a year ago. She is holding a baby and claims it's his. His current girlfriend, Elicia, is not happy with this situation. Oh, she's also the bosses daughter. When Blaine hires Chelsey to be a nanny he forgets all about Elicia. Until the ex-girlfriend returns. And so does the trouble.
author: Tasha Fawkes
